=====General Information=====
Name: ba_stadium
Game: Counter-Strike: Source
Version: 1.1
Author: [Jett]-Willow
Author Email: iammatt@gmail.com
Website: http://www.nothinginc.net
Players: 10+ Recommended, 40 Max

===Release Changes for 1.1==
- Added more cover on right side to make less prone to snipers.
- Changed vehicle models in middle for more cover
- Added barrels in middle to provide cover, and physics fun
- Added advertising for JettLan 3 (http://www.jettlan.net)

=====Map Information========
Program: ValveHammerEditor 4.0
Textures Used:  Standard HL2/CSS Textures
Build Time:  2 Hours (1 Hour For 1.1 Revision)
Compiler:  Standard Valve Hammer Editor , Map Compiling Tools
Compile Time:  4 Minutes 57 Seconds (Original Build), 2 Minutes 3 Seconds for 1.1 Revision

             Compile Computer Specs
CPU:     AMD Barton 2500+ (OCed to 2.2ghz)
RAM:     1024 MB Crucial PC2700 DDR
HDD:     120GB Seagate SATA
GFX:      Nvidia FX5900XT

======Other Information=====
ba_stadium is a BattleArena map for CounterStrikeSource.  This specific BattleArena map takes place in a large stadium.
There are various walls and dividers around the map for cover, along with numerous cars.  BattleArena maps focus on
fast gameplay, frantic firefights, and close knit teamwork to kill the other team as quick as possible.  Be sure to check
out other upcoming BattleArena maps from us!

==Installation Instructions=
Extract the files in this archive to your CSTRIKE FOLDER map directory, or simply extract anywhere you'd like and place them in the example directory below..  The following is an exampleof where it may go: "C:\Program Files\Steam\Steam Apps\xxxx@xxx.xxx\counter-strike source\cstrike".

*Installation*

1. Extract the contents of "prisonship.rar" to your counterstrike source directory,
C:\Program Files\Steam\SteamApps\YOUR USERNAME\counter-strike source


Done, you can now play the Prison Ship map.



Note: This map uses a custom skybox (which I did not create) downloadable from http://www.fpsbanana.com/textures/16



Map - Things you have to know:
*This map is designed as a prison map, 16v16.
*Recommended round time is 9 minute...
*The ship is going to blow up somewhere between 3-6minutes after the round begins, CT must escort T off the ship to safety
 through the tele room (Teleport room). Ts can follow orders or rebel, every man for himself style. Also, whoever gets off 
the ship first controls the base you arrive at.
*Ts cells will sometimes open and sometimes stay close, 50/50 chance and CT will have to go down ad rescue them.
*If someone makes it into the engine room they can switch the power off for 40 seconds, making CT's job harder.

*Certain windows can be shot out, sucking players out of the ship and sealing that section off for 30 seconds.
*Gravity fluctuates, making certain area's passable or nonpassable.
*Tele Room won't open until after 2 minutes.
* Once inside a  teleporter, you can lock people into harness' but once you activate the teleporter with the panel on the wall,
 all harness's close. Make sure you don't block a harness and you must be inside one when it activates.
*Once off the ship, you’re safe. There are two doors where you appear, one is open and leads to where you can look over the base 
and control who goes where. The other leads out to the playground. 
*the playground consists of a digable sandpit, race, Simon says platform, shot for shot arena and the "death room". 
If people fall from the race, fall from the shot for shot arena or dig too far in the arena, they will appear in the 
death room and drown.
*The shot for shot arena can be activated with the button on the wall, once activated you will have 25 seconds to kill your opponent.
After that you are forced into the pit. If you kill your opponent, or the fall in the pit, the arena will close letting you leave. 
MAKE SURE you don't press it when you’re the only one inside.

One day, I decided to make a map where players can take a shield, be a medic to health people or an engineer. These class are available in this map. I use to play at Jail's servers where people use to go to disco or play football. So i put a field where they can play football and voleyball. There is a big disco, an area where Cts can order to go there. 

-Medics can heal other if they are near of people who need their.
-Swats have got a shield.
-Engineers have got a gun with a nice ammo. 

I put some holes where players can stay protected (Pic. 5)

If CTs don't want choose a class there are dispensers of guns or they can just buy the weapons.

Other prison with a high tower, some Weapon dispenser and balls, a buy zone for CTs, a  electric chair,  3 towers for guard  the prisoners, a room for kill people with fire, a disco,some  places where you can  dance,  a field for play football... A nice map where CTs and T can do different things...  (There are 3 weapons at the jails.)
